name: Few Dead Friends / Mari
description: I want to show something personal for me. This is my project "Few Dead Friends". In the project, I scanned my friends, converting their image at that time into a digital version, I scanned them, making them more and more digital. we are getting older every day. only the digital copy remains so. A person's personality is dying a little, they will never be the same as then, that day has passed. we are all a little closer to death.
